description: Moovly Media Inc. develops cloud-based digital media and content creation platform in Canada and Belgium. The company offers Moovly Studio, a video creation editor; Moovly API to add video production to platforms, products, and services; Video Automator to automate the production of videos, as well as to create videos for their customers, products, and services automatically; WordPress plugin to personalize and automate video content; and mobile app to upload video clips, images, and sound files directly to Moovly Studio library. It serves consumers, students, educational institutions, start-ups, SMEs, brands, and blue-chip multinational corporations. Moovly Media Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
